channel.title: Server Status Page
channel.description: I have accidently posted my server with a password I myself don't know of. It will appear soon with a description of spam and I will not be able to edit it. The server is up 24.7 therefore won't disappear of the server status list and will be stuck there for weeks. Please, can a [b]moderator[/b] delete it, assist me.

item.title: Server Status Page
item.dc:creator: @public_boolean public boolean
item.description:
@public_boolean wrote:

The best thing to do is close your VPS host, or stop it until it goes away from the status page,
Then re-add it.

In future read before doing anything.
